sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as Presentation API
    participant BL as Business Logic
    participant DB as Persistence Database
    participant Email as ConfirmationEmail

    opt User Registration
        User->>API: Fill registration form
        API->>BL: Submit user data
        BL->>DB: Create user
        DB-->>BL: OK
        BL->>Email: Send welcome email
        Email-->>User: Confirmation email
        BL-->>API: Success
        API-->>User: Welcome message
    end

    opt Place Creation
        User->>API: Submit place data
        Note over User, API: User must be authenticated
        API->>BL: Create place
        BL->>DB: Store place
        DB-->>BL: OK
        BL-->>API: Place created
        API-->>User: Success message
    end

    opt Review Submission
        User->>API: Submit review
        Note over User, API: User must be authenticated
        API->>BL: Create review
        BL->>DB: Store review
        DB-->>BL: OK
        BL-->>API: Review linked
        API-->>User: Success message
    end

    opt Fetch Places
        User->>API: Search places
        API->>BL: Apply filters
        BL->>DB: Query places
        DB-->>BL: Results
        BL-->>API: Formatted data
        API-->>User: Show places
    end
